OL,5,G2100 Nick Knowles in South America
OL,6,     FIntrepid Nick Knowles begins his
OL,7,     Flatest adventure clinging to a
OL,8,     Frock in the Andes mountains, and
OL,9,     Fmeets indigenous people, penguins,
OL,10,     Fand inspirational cyclist Dimitri
OL,11,     FPoffe. (Ep1/3)
OL,12,G2200 Michael Palin in Nigeria
OL,13,     FIn the first leg of an epic 1300
OL,14,     Fmiles across Nigeria, Michael is
OL,15,     Fin bustling Lagos and an
OL,16,     Fextraordinary waterfront slum
OL,17,     Fschool, then dodges alligators at
OL,18,     Fthe Emir of Kano's palace. (Ep1/3)
