OL,5,G0110 Dogs Behaving (Very) Badly
OL,6,     FFrenchie Bingo is stopping Alan
OL,7,     Ffrom finding romance. Can Graeme
OL,8,     FHall help Alan find love? And
OL,9,     FCockerpoo Molly cries at the top
OL,10,     Fof her voice. Sleep deprived mum
OL,11,     FAmy is at her wit's end.
OL,12,G0210 Into Death Valley with Nick
OL,13,G     Knowles
OL,14,     FIn the hottest place on Earth,
OL,15,     FNick goes sand buggy driving, and
OL,16,     Fexperiences dawn at Zabriskie
OL,17,     FPoint with amazing views of craggy
OL,18,     Fmountains, dunes and salt flats.
